<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/jul/26/">&#x27a0;</a> July 26, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="beautiful-code" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://amazon.com/o/ASIN/0596510047/groovymother-20/ref=nosim/">Beautiful Code: Leading Programmers Explain How They Think</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Just picked this up, and a quick skim shows it&#8217;s something a bit special:  Learn good coding practices by reading experts choice of &#8220;the most beautiful code they&#8217;ve seen&#8221;, with plenty of commentary.  I&#8217;m halfway tempted to take a day off next week and just sit and read this all day.</p>

